OL,3,CNI Children's Hospice to reduce bed
OL,4,Ccapacity due to 'loss of funding'
OL,6,FA statement from the charity said the
OL,7,Freduction is "deeply regrettable and
OL,8,Fmay potentially incur a decrease in
OL,9,Fstaff numbers and a new working model".
OL,11,FThe long-term future of the service
OL,12,Fwill be protected and the number of
OL,13,Fchildren and families supported will
OL,14,Fstay the same.
OL,16,FThe organisation is consulting with
OL,17,Fstaff members and service users who
OL,18,Fmight be affected.
