OL,3,CNI Children's Hospice to reduce bed
OL,4,Ccapacity due to 'loss of funding'
OL,6,FThe announcement came as MLAs gathered
OL,7,Fat the Stormont Assembly to call on
OL,8,Fthe Prime Minister to give Northern
OL,9,FIreland the "resources that it needs
OL,10,Fto deliver effective public services".
OL,12,FMembers will debate a motion urging
OL,13,Fthe Government to put Northern
OL,14,FIreland's finances on a "sustainable
OL,15,Ffooting".
OL,17,FFirst Minister Michelle O'Neill,
OL,18,Fspeaking at the start of the sitting
OL,19,Fon Tuesday morning, expressed concern.
