OL,3,CNI Children's Hospice to reduce bed
OL,4,Ccapacity due to 'loss of funding'
OL,6,FGrace Stewart, acting director of
OL,7,FChildren's Hospice, said she
OL,8,Fprofoundly regretted having to
OL,9,Fimplement any reduction in capacity.
OL,11,FShe said: "This decision, led by the
OL,12,Fneed to ensure the long-term
OL,13,Fsustainability of our service, will
OL,14,Fimpact bed numbers and availability.
OL,16,F"Given the loss of government funding
OL,17,Ffor one of our beds, our intention is
OL,18,Fto run six beds Monday to Friday and
OL,19,Fthree beds Saturday and Sunday.
