OL,6,F"This is a change from our seven beds,
OL,7,Fseven nights model."
OL,9,F"Despite these challenges, our
OL,10,Funwavering commitment to supporting
OL,11,Fchildren and their families remains."
OL,13,FThe hospice requires more than
OL,14,F#20million annually to provide its
OL,15,Fservices.
OL,17,FThe charity said it was facing "severe
OL,18,Ffinancial challenges due to the
OL,19,Fcurrent economic climate".
